snippet.title: Android Simulator - Announcement Trailer | STEAM
snippet.description:
Android Simulator sign up for free Steam Playtest now! 👇
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1891250/Android_Simulator/

Be the first to play the game 👉 sign up now for Steam Playtest! 🦾 The game is created on the latest Unreal Engine 5, which allowed us to achieve extremely high quality gameplay, and you will be able to play the game soon on Steam.

-«  About Android Simulator  »-

Android Simulator is a futuristic FPS game in which you take the role of an android who is in charge of a spaceship colony. Keep a firm hand on the flight route and manage the right water balance for plants, oxygen level, and spacecraft parameters to securely deliver the colonizers.

#AndroidSimulator #ue5 #unrealengine5
